{"tid":2292142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有冇人知呢隻汪汪有冇違反人權法","createTime":"2020-11-19T09:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T09:37:20.000Z","uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b357d9875e38005f8fe035642810e2215ca3dfe","tid":2292142,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"19/11/2019 <br />\n- 速龍小巴衝向人群　汪威遜：揸得快唔代表唔安全<br />\n速龍小隊今日凌晨在油麻地驅散示威者，片段拍攝到有接載警員的白色小巴全速衝向人群，據報釀成人踩人，導致多人受傷。行動部高級警司汪威遜今日於記者會上稱「揸得快唔代表唔安全（drive fast doesn't mean it's unsafe）」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O01Swzj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO01Swzj.jpg&h=1b09b067&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2068c97076d528cd0269367cde0e8b0aa4a5b62e","tid":2292142,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"322a8e97e0009511d3457caffc2d69f3f492fd1b","tid":2292142,"uid":216239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"算把啦 咪又係無事"}]}